dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints, shading, and spot heights. Depths shown by gradient tints, isolines, and soundings. Map shows prefecture boundaries, two classes of railroads, roads, main air routes, lighthouses, volcanoes, temples, tourist sites. Ancillary maps: Nanpō (southern) -- Nansei (southwest) Islands. Includes location map. "Approved by the Geographical Survey Institute of the Ministry of Construction, Japan (1962- No. 1193)".
dct_publisher_sm: Tokyo : Midorikawa Map Printing Co. Ltd., 1962.
